(44, 2, 27, 43, 11, 39, 39, 'see corruption', 'Resurrection and Corruption', 'This connection highlights the theme of resurrection, as Acts 2:27 speaks of not allowing the Holy One to see corruption, while John 11:39 emphasizes the decay of Lazarus after four days of death. Both passages underscore the contrast between life and death.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 2, 27, 46, 15, 52, 52, 'see corruption', 'Resurrection and Incorruption', 'This connection highlights the theme of resurrection and the transformation of the dead. Acts 2:27 speaks of not seeing corruption, while 1 Corinthians 15:52 emphasizes being raised incorruptible.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 2, 28, 19, 16, 11, 11, 'full of joy with thy countenance', 'Joy in God''s Presence', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of joy found in God''s presence. Acts 2:28 reflects the joy of life, while Psalms 16:11 explicitly states that joy is found in God''s presence.', 'theme', 0.412, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 2, 28, 19, 25, 4, 4, 'ways of life', 'Connection of Divine Guidance', 'Both passages emphasize the desire for divine instruction and guidance. Acts 2:28 speaks of knowing the ''ways of life,'' while Psalms 25:4 requests to be shown ''thy ways.''', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 2, 28, 20, 2, 19, 19, 'ways of life', 'Paths of Life Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of life and joy. Acts 2:28 speaks of the ''ways of life'' leading to joy, while Proverbs 2:19 warns that those who do not follow the right paths do not return, emphasizing the importance of choosing the correct way.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 2, 28, 43, 11, 25, 26, 'full of joy with thy countenance', 'Connection of Life and Joy', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of life and joy. Acts 2:28 speaks of being made full of joy, while John 11:25-26 declares Jesus as the resurrection and the life, suggesting that belief in Him leads to eternal joy and life.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
