(44, 2, 30, 24, 33, 14, 15, 'of the fruit of his loins', 'Connection of Davidic Promises', 'This connection highlights the promise of God to raise up a leader from David''s lineage. Both passages emphasize the fulfillment of God''s oath regarding the establishment of a righteous ruler from David''s line.', 'prophecy', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
